    {
      "id": "619ca1c6-e287-4529-aeca-41bef38c84be",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Flipped classrooms are better suited for learners with developed SRL skills. Authors work focuses on measuring effect of study regularity on academic success. The work defines a measure of study regularity that can uncover learner profiles in B-Learning. This measure heavily correlates with academic success.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
